snippet.title: Nekole Amber
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel! My name is Nekole and I am a licensed pediatric occupational therapist, as well as a parenting & soul-alignment mentor. 

Here you will learn all about the power of parenting intentionally, how to soulfully support your child's development, and from time to time, some quality recommendations for products I LOVE!

I'm passionate about supporting you in your motherhood journey! I offer deeper levels of support through my online courses and programs, a mastermind community, and my private mentorship packages. If you're interested in learning more check out my website below, or email me at hello@nekoleamber.com.

Xx

::::::Follow Me:::::

*Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/nekole.amber/
*Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/nekole.amber
*Website - https://www.nekoleamber.com/

-Nekole
